{"title":"Dry Fruits Mithai","description":"","products":[{"product_id":"kaju-katli","title":"Kaju Katli","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"pro-des-title pro-info-box\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003ch2 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(137, 6, 12);\"\u003eIndia’s Favourite Sweet \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/h2\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIndulge in the sublime taste of Dadu’s Kaju Katli, made with premium large-size cashew nuts, pure ghee, and \u003cstrong\u003eminimal sugar approach\u003c\/strong\u003e that allows the natural sweetness of cashews to shine. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(137, 6, 12);\"\u003e\u003ca style=\"color: rgb(137, 6, 12);\" href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/reel\/CuCp3RfvwpG\/?igsh=czc1bng5d2h4Z3ll\" title=\"Watch how Dadu's Premium Kaju Katli is made online\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eWatch\u003c\/a\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e the Craftsmanship in Action\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch3 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(137, 6, 12);\"\u003eKey Features\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003ch4 dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\n\u003cspan\u003eFinest Ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003eMade with organic large-sized cashew nuts, the purest desi ghee, and adorned with pure vegetarian silver leaf. Our silver leaf (varak) is meticulously crafted by skilled artisans through a unique process, ensuring unmatched quality and elegance in every piece. \u003ca rel=\"noopener\" title=\"Learn more about Dadu's Kaju Katli\" href=\"https:\/\/dadus.co.in\/blogs\/explore-dadus\/kaju-katli\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(137, 6, 12);\"\u003eLearn More\u003c\/span\u003e.\u003c\/a\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4 dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMinimalist Sugar Approach \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003eA healthier treat emphasizing the natural sweetness of cashews over sugar.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4 dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https:\/\/dadus.co.in\/products\/sugarfree-kajukatli?_pos=3\u0026amp;_psq=sugarfree\u0026amp;_ss=e\u0026amp;_v=1.0\" title=\"Shop Sugar Free Kaju Katli from Dadu's\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSugar-Free Options\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/a\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eEnjoy the same great taste without added sugar.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch3 dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(137, 6, 12);\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eOrder Today\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/h3\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eShop your favorite sweets online and enjoy our reliable delivery service. For a free tasting and a true gourmet experience, visit Dadu’s near you.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp dir=\"ltr\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFor international shipping inquiries, contact our support. Our clients within Hyderabad, India can get instant delivery using \u003ca title=\"Shop Dadu's Sweets Collection on Swiggy and get instant delivery\" href=\"https:\/\/www.swiggy.com\/menu\/2085?source=sharing\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(137, 6, 12);\"\u003eSwiggy\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/a\u003e or \u003ca rel=\"noopener\" title=\"SHOP Dadu's Sweet Collection on Zomato and get Instant Delivery\" href=\"https:\/\/zomato.onelink.me\/xqzv\/h1s29802\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"color: rgb(137, 6, 12);\"\u003eZomato\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/a\u003e.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Dadu’s (Indian Mithai)","offers":[{"title":"250 Gms","offer_id":45